{"tid":1794101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"ESPN引CCTV消息：若奧斯爾不再上陣　將復播阿仙奴","createTime":"2019-12-23T01:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T01:43:19.000Z","uid":227801,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9ed924fb4e8fa7b8c00288277bc6a8e3e34c6a","tid":1794101,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499117-20191223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499117-20191223.htm&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=4ac87d5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499117-20191223.htm&h=14329958\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499117-20191223.htm</a><br />\n效力英超阿仙奴的德國球員奧斯爾，早前發表聲援中國新疆維吾爾人的言論之後，內地中央電視台取消直播阿仙奴對曼城的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n在過去星期六，阿仙奴主場與愛華頓賽和0:0的賽事，賽前公布的陣容中，未有包括奧斯爾。根據體育頻道ESPN報道，央視突然在網上直播這場賽事，只提供英語旁述。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述央視的消息指出，若果阿仙奴由今個星期四對般尼茅夫的賽事開始，不再派出奧斯爾上陣，央視將會繼續播放阿仙奴的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴領隊龍格堡早前表示，奧斯爾未有被列入對愛華頓的賽事，因為狀態不足，以及上一場對曼城的賽事態度有問題。"},{"pid":"ba4a899d1422243e7b30e853a0b3b902765984a8","tid":1794101,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"支那已經統治地球。。。"},{"pid":"b0109cc06ee2e92d8425c80c11cc4fed4668f9fd","tid":1794101,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7804eb6bad57e3a08df4b87a8cca6bdb275f7bea","tid":1794101,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴一跪即PK"},{"pid":"75566788c1f59b2ebe6f1ab69644ca756cb9cd35","tid":1794101,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:29:43.000Z","msg":"今次叫奧斯爾<br />\n下次叫美斯 牙朗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo